OL,3,CFunding sign-off delayed for new
OL,4,CShields Ferry landing
OL,6,FThe final sign-off on funding to
OL,7,Fsecure the future of the Shields Ferry
OL,8,Fhas been delayed.
OL,10,FIt was anticipated that members of the
OL,11,FNorth East Joint Transport Committee
OL,12,Fwould give the green light to the
OL,13,Frelease of #4.58 million for a new
OL,14,Fferry landing in North Shields at a
OL,15,Fmeeting on Tuesday (16 April).
OL,17,FHowever, due to a number of absences
OL,18,Famong councillors, the meeting was
OL,19,F"inquorate" ` meaning the decision
OL,20,Fcould not be taken.
