OL,3,CFunding sign-off delayed for new
OL,4,CShields Ferry landing
OL,6,FBecause the meeting was the
OL,7,Fcommittee's last before the new North
OL,8,FEast Combined Authority is formed next
OL,9,Fmonth, an additional meeting of the
OL,10,FJoint Transport Committee's Tyne and
OL,11,FWear Sub Committee will be convened to
OL,12,Fmake the decision. A date for this has
OL,13,Fnot yet been set.
OL,15,FThere was an opportunity for members
OL,16,Fto debate the issue and ask questions
OL,17,Fto offer guidance to officers, but
OL,18,Fnobody chose to speak.
