OL,3,CFunding sign-off delayed for new
OL,4,CShields Ferry landing
OL,6,FThe cash was left over from the major
OL,7,FTyne and Wear Metro Flow project,
OL,8,Fwhich saw single track sections of the
OL,9,FMetro line to South Shields dualled in
OL,10,F2022.
OL,12,FThe existing jetty in North Shields is
OL,13,Fdue to fall into an unusable state as
OL,14,Fearly as next year, leading to
OL,15,Fquestions about the future of the
OL,16,Fferry crossing.
OL,18,FPlans have been in the works for some
OL,19,Fyears to relocate the terminal to a
OL,20,Fnew location next to the North Shields
OL,21,FFish Quay.
