OL,4,CShields Ferry landing
OL,6,FHowever, the project has suffered
OL,7,Fseveral setbacks and the delays have
OL,8,Fseen costs spiral to almost #15
OL,9,Fmillion due to inflation.
OL,11,FWhile there is still a considerable
OL,12,Famount of that #15 million still to be
OL,13,Ffound, there is confidence this will
OL,14,Fcome later this year once the new
OL,15,FNorth East Mayor is elected next month.
