OL,6,FRegional transport chiefs have asked
OL,7,Ffor the Government to "accelerate"
OL,8,F#8.1 million of the City Region
OL,9,FSustainable Transport Settlement
OL,10,F(CRSTS) that will be given to the
OL,11,Fincoming mayor, which is widely
OL,12,Fexpected to be approved.
OL,14,FElsewhere, Nexus and the North East
OL,15,FLocal Enterprise Partnership are also
OL,16,Fcommitting money to the new ferry
OL,17,Flanding, with Nexus planning to pay
OL,18,F#1.3 million towards the scheme and
OL,19,Fthe North East Local Enterprise
OL,20,FPartnership putting in almost #300,000.
